metadata.name: Rosa Pastel
metadata.description:
Rosa Pastel is an urban pop/rnb track created in collaboration with my friend and producer Bulla Beatz during a creative camp on Medellin Colombia some years ago. 

Bulla Beatz is a Colombian producer and the one in charge of produce some of my songs as ‘’Shot por mi’’ , ‘’Mi Vieja Chica’’ & ‘’Clavada’’. If sometime  you heard one of this songs, you already know that his style is something extraordinary and unique

The creative process of work with Bulla Beatz is something outstanding, we can create and create music for hours with non stop; I remember one time during the camp that we created and recorded 3 songs in one day;Rosa Pastel was one of them, We hope you like it!

Collector rewards on: alexpaul.xyz/rosapastel
